h as Exhibition, Playoffs and Season and the ability to let friends go head-to-head. Then CNN sportscaster Van Earl Wright lends his voice talents to the game for in game commentary.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46820,39665,101684,101567,101100,100907,100887,100879,100863,100832],"tags":[268435470],"category":0,"genres":[14],"first_release_date":791596800000,"platforms":[50],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":50,"date":791596800000,"region":8,"human":"1995-Feb-01","y":1995,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/o3fvgblmal0f1kbkrotr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"o3fvgblmal0f1kbkrotr","width":1518,"height":2156}},{"id":39018,"name":"Jammit","slug":"jammit","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/jammit","created_at":1498118273587,"updated_at":1511736798042,"summary":"Whiners, better give this game a miss, 'cause Jammit's the closest thing you'll ever find to real street hoops. Don't even think of looking for an official--in this game, it's jam-or-be-jammed--and great D leaves the opposition gasping. In Intensive Care. \n \nStep onto one of the five stylin' courts, and the air show begins. Revers jams. Fade-away jumpers. And way more attitude--and altitude--than you'll ever find in the so-called pros. \n \nGet past our three asphalt warriors, and we'll send you to meet the Judge, and you'd better bring your license to drive. Put some money down, talk a little trash, then walk the walk. Or else you'll watch yourself getting faced on our exclusive Slam Cam... \n \nThese guys don't even know how to spell \"foul.\" \n \nMastered one on one? There are six more game variations out there, chump. \n \nWhen you go to the hoop, the Slam Cam zooms in on the action. \nReasons to lay down the cash: \n \n-\"The Slam Cam\"--get up-close-and-impersonal as players drive the lane \n-Over 700 frames of digitized animation \n-Five graffiti covered basketball courts \n-Side bets, 'cause only money really talks \n-Enough digitized trash talk to dis the entire neighborhood \n-Seven different streetball games: Sweat, 1-on-1, 2 Hot, Poison, Slams Only, in-2-it and Frenzy","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46820,39665,101684,101567,101100,100907,100887,100879,100863,100832],"tags":[268435470],"category":0,"genres":[14],"first_release_date":760060800000,"platforms":[50],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":50,"date":760060800000,"region":8,"human":"1994-Feb-01","y":1994,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/equbi69ftlv1f3oac8sk.jpg","cloudinary_id":"equbi69ftlv1f3oac8sk","width":1135,"height":2156}},{"id":39019,"name":"Dennis Miller: That's News to Me","slug":"dennis-miller-thats-news-to-me","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dennis-miller-thats-news-to-me","created_at":1498118276455,"updated_at":1515842192074,"summary":"Before the kids and the mortgage and the job that requires a tie, there was Saturday Night Live Weekend Update with Dennis Miller, the coolest newscaster to hit the airwaves. Well, he's back and this ain't no re-run. In fact, it's not like television at all (okay, the quality of the digital video is pretty much the same). It's interactive, it's entertaining, it doesn't have commercials. What it does have is more than 200 topics in 4 categories - world news, politics, sports and show biz - that you select from. Pick a month, pick a topic. Now sit back and watch Dennis lampoon and lambast everything from the bombing of the World Trade Center in New York City to the bombing of Arnold Schwarzenegger in \"Last Action Hero.\" As Dennis says, \"It's a trip through the historical carnage that was.\"","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[13189,15911,25222,22425,76098,41895,60,55803,51464,11296],"tags":[27,268435487,536871262,536871684,536871939,536875054,536875139,536876292,536876663],"category":0,"keywords":[350,772,1027,4142,4227,5380,5751],"themes":[27],"genres":[31],"first_release_date":760060800000,"platforms":[50],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":50,"date":7