 fangs and a scrying glass. Then you must trek through the misty wood until you find the abode of the Witch of Good. Give them to her. and she will give you fire protection in return. \n \nThe second verse tells you that if you find the \"man of solitary means\" he will give you a map. However, this map is hard to decipher, but is meant to help you get safely through the forest \n \nTucky makes his way around the forest, encountering all manner of nasty creatures. They shoot at him and he can fight back by throwing swords and, if he finds them, other weapons. \n \nI like this game very much. It has given me many hours of pleasure. It is easy to get into, yet difficult to get out of. I still don't know how the scoring works. I think it works on tasks done\" like the first pan of Short Circuit. Graphics, although simple and single-colour-ed, are still ample for the game and do not detract from the overall appeal. Sound is just the standard bang-bang.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39107,"name":"La Diosa de Cozumel","slug":"la-diosa-de-cozumel","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/la-diosa-de-cozumel","created_at":1498120174025,"updated_at":1515673779641,"summary":"The first game in the Ci-U-Than Spanish language text adventure series.","collection":4913,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[81535,80514,80508,80480,80070,80069,79659,79451,79064,78419],"tags":[536873308,536875172],"category":0,"keywords":[2396,4260],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/euiw3nifbascgbuhq9mx.jpg","cloudinary_id":"euiw3nifbascgbuhq9mx","width":573,"height":683}},{"id":39108,"name":"Cosa Nostra","slug":"cosa-nostra","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cosa-nostra","created_at":1498120177156,"updated_at":1515592505373,"summary":"Has de buscar por las 92 pantallas de Chicago a los cinco grandes capos y eliminarlos. Antes de llegar a ellos, habrás de combatir contra sus esbirros y al eliminarlos coger sus municiones, ya que las tuyas no son eternas.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,34919,40524,23175,16468,1070,2940,68324,28029,37022],"tags":[1,536871127],"category":0,"keywords":[215],"themes":[1]},{"id":39109,"name":"Codename Mat 3D","slug":"codename-mat-3d","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/codename-mat-3d","created_at":1498120193302,"updated_at":1500208601454,"summary":"Codename MAT - MISSION: ALIEN TERMINATION - the desperate plan to place in the \nmind of a teenager the combined tactical skills of all the planetary leaders in \nthe solar system. MAT is mankind's last hope. \n \nFor decades the Myons have sought to dominate the Solar System, whose fleets \nare now ragged and depleted. They have launched an all-or-nothing attack, \nknowing that Earth is developing revolutionary space-craft. Only the prototype \n- USS Centurion - has been built, and it must be pressed into immediate service \nas both battle-cruiser and tactical command centre. \n \nPiloting the craft in battle and controlling the Planetary Defence Fleets is \nbeyond any normal human... MAT is created. \n \nNow your mind is MAT's mind. Take control of the Centurion and blast off on the \ngreatest adventure of all...","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[44242,24491,28465,75579,75275,34919,75102,33603,36962,55888],"tags":[268435469],"category":0,"genres":[13]},{"id":39110,"name":"Cobras Arc","slug":"cobras-arc","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cobras-arc","created_at":1498120194828,"updated_at":1521827947945,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":39111,"name":"Cobra Stallone","slug":"cobra-stallone","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cobra-stallone","created_at":1498120197440,"updated_at":1500212372743,"summary":"Crime is a disease. He's the cure. \n \nThe Cobra strikes! \n\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\" \nAs vigilante cop, Marion Cobretti of the 'Zombie Squad', you must \nrescue top fashion model Ingrid Knutsen from an army of psychotic \nkillers and the evil clutches of 'The Night Slasher'. \n \nThe Game \n\"\"\"\"\"\"\"\" \nThsi is where the law stops ... and you start \n \nAdvance through three playfields. \nCITY SCENE (night-time), RURAL AREA (day-time) and FACTORY. Use \nplatforms and levels to locate and protect Ingrid from her attackers \nin each stage. \nUse 'HEAD-BUTT' feature to defend yourself and collect limited weapons \nhidden inside BEEF BURGERS to thwart the attack, beware - each weapon \nonly lasts a short while! \n \nWeapons are: INVINCIBLILITY PILL \n    KNIFE \n    PISTOL \n    LASER SIGHTED MACHINE GUN \nTo move to the next section ou must: \n 1. Collect 'all four' beef burger weapons. \n 2. Rescue Ingrid (she will follow you if you touch her). \n 3. Clear the section of killers.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39112,"name":"Le Chevalier Blanc","slug":"le-chevalier-blanc","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/le-chevalier-blanc","created_at":1498120200429,"updated_at":1500208535493,"summary":"Le Jeu : \n \nAngola : Monseigneur, je dois la vie au Chevalier blanc. C'est lui qui m'a \nsauvé des griffes des monstres du chateau. \n \nLe Roi : Chevalier par queUe magie as-tu réussi ce prodige. Personne n'est \njamais revenu de là-bas! \n \nChevalier blanc : Ah! Monseigneur, il fallait que voire fille soit aussi \nbelle et que votre bras soit puissant pour m'armer de courage car la bataille \nfut terrible. Votre fille m'avait demandé de l'escorter dans les champs afin \nde cueillir un bouquet lorsque nous f�mes assaillis par les monstres de la \nforêt. \n \nJ'eus beau en tuer une dizaine, ils réussirent à me ravir voire fille et mes \narmes. \n \nJe pris alors mon courage dans une main et capturai un cheval de l'autre. \nNous travers�mes les marais o� les monstres, sans doute fatigués par les \nmorsures de voire fille, avaient abandonné là mes armes. Lorsque je fus devant \nle ch�teau, je donnais à mon cheval des fleurs magiques gr�ce auxquelles il \nfil un bon fabuleux au-dessus du pont levis. Alors je dus visiter le ch�teau \net me battre contre mille démons pour ramener la princesse. Pour récupérer les \narmes dans les marais : on ne peut prendre que les armes qui clignotent. Elles \nsont indispensables pour passer au tableau suivant.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39113,"name":"Cheril of the bosque","slug":"cheril-of-the-bosque","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cheril-of-the-bosque","created_at":1498120202203,"updated_at":1500208524242,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39114,"name":"Charly Diams","slug":"charly-diams","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/charly-diams","created_at":1498120205446,"updated_at":1500208513045,"summary":"Tu misión es localizar el escondrijo de los mil diamantes azules. \nPara ello previamente deberas descubrir y recoger las siete flores milagrosas, diseminadas por el mundo. \nDesde el golfo del Bengala al desierto del Sahara, del corazón de Francia a la cordillera de los Andes, desde el lago Titicaca a los más dispares lugares, el camino es largo. Largo y peligroso porque deberás escapar a todas las trampas que te tenderán los hombres y los elementos para evitar que te hagas con el fabuloso tesoro.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/dojmvpbo70fuvtvzyshu.jpg","cloudinary_id":"dojmvpbo70fuvtvzyshu","width":1174,"height":1444}},{"id":39115,"name":"Chamonix Challenge","slug":"chamonix-challenge","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/chamonix-challenge","created_at":1498120207345,"updated_at":1503311371749,"summary":"El primer juego de simulación de alpinismo con un realismo que te sorprenderá. \nEncontrarás todos los elementos que caracterizan una ruta de montaña: duración (día y noche), estación, consistencia de la nieve, fatiga, supervivencia, peligros, paisajes impresionantes, abismos, glaciares, etc. \nDesde el principio, el jugador debe equipar al alpinista con todo aquell