y use the power of one at a time. The masks can also be exchanged at certain points in the game. This game received the best reviews of the trilogy, despite the deviation from the franchise's storyline and style.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[68287,28029,36950,64204,142,71455,27314,27523,25300,14364],"tags":[1,18,268435461,536871882,536871937,536875054],"category":0,"keywords":[970,1025,4142],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[5]},{"id":39125,"name":"Mask II","slug":"mask-ii","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/mask-ii","created_at":1498120620582,"updated_at":1515772499088,"summary":"MASK II is a 2D horizontal scrolling shoot-em-up. The game featured many more of the M.A.S.K. vehicles, and included a selection process in which the player chose which vehicles to use before the game began. Only one vehicle could be controlled at a time but these could be quickly interchanged. Again, the game was received favorably in the press, where it was noted that it was a better tie-in to the franchise than the first, because it featured more of the vehicles","collection":2846,"franchise":1040,"franchises":[1040],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[28029,68287,36950,64204,76246,27314,10039,19341,25311,76722],"tags":[1,18,268435461,536871037,536872360,536872983,1073741828],"developers":[3212],"publishers":[3212],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[125,1448,2071],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[5],"first_release_date":567907200000,"platforms":[15,26,25,27],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":26,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":27,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"MASK 2","comment":"Other"},{"name":"MASK TWO","comment":"Other"},{"name":"Mobile Armored Strike Kommand II","comment":"Other"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ol8uchdug4bxiudao5tr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ol8uchdug4bxiudao5tr","width":1000,"height":1280}},{"id":39126,"name":"Mask","slug":"mask","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/mask","created_at":1498120623653,"updated_at":1517270595336,"summary":"MASK is a vertically-viewed 2D game in which the player controls the Thunderhawk vehicle. The premise of the game is that V.E.N.O.M. have propelled Boulder Hill into a time vortex, and the player must rescue the other members of the M.A.S.K. team by collecting and re-assembling parts of a scan key, which then directs the player to the location of the missing personnel. The game received mostly favorable reviews at the time, although it was noted by some that the tie-in to the franchise was quite tenuous and only the graphics, rather than the storyline and gameplay, connected it to the M.A.S.K. franchise.","collection":2846,"franchise":1040,"franchises":[1040],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[68287,28029,36950,64204,27314,71455,25300,142,11253,10039],"tags":[1,18,268435461,268435489,536871037,536871882,536872360,1073741827],"developers":[3212],"publishers":[3212],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[3],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[125,970,1448],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[5,33],"first_release_date":567907200000,"platforms":[15,26,25],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":26,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987-Dec-31","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Mobile Armored Strike Kommand","comment":"Other"},{"name":"MASK"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gzbmcekryjupnn8bjmfo.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gzbmcekryjupnn8bjmfo","width":1000,"height":1276}},{"id":39127,"name":"Rambo - First Blood Part 2","slug":"rambo-first-blood-part-2","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/rambo-first-blood-part-2","created_at":1498120800024,"updated_at":1503285140880,"summary":"Tough Vietnam veteran John Rambo is called back into action after some soldiers are taken hostage in a PoW camp. His orders are to simply capture photographic evidence of the war crimes taking place, but after finding a close friend tied up, he decides to wipe them all out by himself. This being Hollywood, chances are that he will succeed. \n \nSEGA's interpretation of his challenge recreates Commando fairly closely. You move up the screen, taking out enemies – these respawn, so there is no value in not moving upwards as quickly as possible. Find strategic positions from which to attack. Touch each hostage you find to free them. \n \nYou have knives and grenades, but using the latter alerts the enemy as to your presence, making life harder. Extra weapons such as rocket launchers and machine guns can be collected en route.","franchise":165,"franchises":[165],"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[28029,76246,19341,10039,76229,68287,32902,17446,36594,68142],"tags":[1,39,268435461,268435489,536872198,1073741827],"developers":[11739],"publishers":[11739],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[3],"game_modes":[1,2],"keywords":[1286],"themes":[1,39],"genres":[5,33],"first_release_date":532483200000,"platforms":[64],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":64,"date":532483200000,"region":5,"human":"1986-Nov-16","y":1986,"m":11}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Ashura","comment":"Japanese title"},{"name":"Secret Command"},{"name":"Secret Commando","comment":"European title"},{"name":"阿修羅","comment":"Japanese spelling"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/kzohvfjmegz8d49sguwh.jpg","cloudinary_id":"kzohvfjmegz8d49sguwh","width":1000,"height":1391},"esrb":{"rating":4}},{"id":39128,"name":"Welcome to Amsoft Side A","slug":"welcome-to-amsoft-side-a","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/welcome-to-amsoft-side-a","created_at":1498120800729,"updated_at":1500209881010,"summary":"When a user bought a 464 (tape) model of Amstrad/Schneider CPC there was a demo tape in the box. \n \nSame with disk (664/6128) models, there was a demo disc included, that was later changed with games. \n \nThe tape offered a short and simplistic demonstration of the CPC's graphical and sound capabilities, promoting the fact that the CPC was a good all-aroun machine, equally for business and games.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39129,"name":"Welcome to Amsoft Side B","slug":"welcome-to-amsoft-side-b","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/welcome-to-amsoft-side-b","created_at":1498120803899,"updated_at":1500209893875,"summary":"When a user bought a 464 (tape) model of Amstrad/Schneider CPC there was a demo tape in the box. \n \nSame with disk (664/6128) models, there was a demo disc included, that was later changed with games. \n \nThe tape offered a short and simplistic demonstration of the CPC's graphical and sound capabilities, promoting the fact that the CPC was a good all-aroun machine, equally for business and games.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39130,"name":"Pulsator","slug":"pulsator","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/pulsator","created_at":1498120807077,"updated_at":1500210003605,"summary":"Tu Pulsator no tiene opción Ha sido colocado en el centro de una serie de laberintos altamente peligrosos. Para escapar, debe rescatar a los cinco «pulsies», cada uno de los cuales está cautivo en un nivel distinto del laberinto. \nPero no está solo. Una gran variedad de Pulsators enemigos patrullan por el laberinto, cada cual más inteligente y mortífero, con su peculiar manera de hacerte la vida más difícil. \nHay cinco niveles en el juego, cada uno de 49 salas. Tienes que completar un nivel antes de poder llevar a tu Pulsator al siguiente. En cada nivel hay un «Pulsie» que rescatar. Esto se hace encontrando la llave que abrirá la puerta de su cárcel. \nLos Pulsators enemigos se hacen más peligrosos con cada nivel que alcances. El laberinto también se hace más difícil según cambias de nivel. \nEl juego es bastante más complejo de lo que parece, no es cuestión de liarse a tiros y de encontrar la salida del laberinto. Hay seis tipos de puertas, numeradas del uno al seis, que se pueden abrir o cerrar pasando sobre unos sensores. Los sensores también están numerados de uno a seis. Si un tipo de puerta está cerrada y pasas sobre su sensor correspondiente, la puerta se abrirá. Sin embargo, si la puerta está abierta, pasando sobre el sensor, la cerrará.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":39131,"name":"Psycho Pigs UXB","slug":"psycho-pigs-uxb","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/psycho-pigs-uxb","created_at":1498120808235,"updated_at":1506317665305,"summary":"El jugador controla a un cerdo y el objetivo del juego es explotar a otros cerdos tirándoles bombas. Las bombas son generadas aleatoriamente por el mapa y pueden ser recogidas y arrojadas a los demás cerdos. A las bombas se les da un número entre 5 y 30; cuando la bomba es lanzada toma ese número de segundos para explotar. Las bombas que directamente golpean cerdos explotan en contacto. Varios poderes están disponibles en todas partes del juego como el gas que hace que todos los otros personajes se duerman. \n \nUn mini-juego de bonificación consiste en cerdos apareciendo aleatoriamente desde unos agujeros, y el jugador debe golpearlos devuelta hace abajo del agujero con su propio cerdo, en un modo de juego similar a Whac-A-Mole.","popularity":1.666666666666667,"tags":[1073741827],"developers":[13510,303],"publishers":[10317,227,303],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[3],"game_modes":[1,2],"themes":[1],"genres":[33],"first_release_date":567907200000,"platforms":[52,121,15,26,25,27],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":26,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12},{"category":0,"platform":121,"date":751852800000,"region":5,"human":"1993-Oct-29","y":1993,"m":10},{"category":2,"platform":27,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":52,"date":567907200000,"region":5,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Butasan"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qmemqrebjn5xvb1gfdza.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qmemqrebjn5xvb1gfdza","width":1000,"height":1291}},{"id":39132,"name":"The Race Against Time","slug":"the-race-against-time","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/the-race-against-time","created_at":1498120810755,"updated_at":1515733601395,"summary":"LA CARRERA CONTRA EL TIEMPO \nEn el juego tomas la persona de Ornar Khalifa, el legendario corredor sudanés. Debes recorrer el mundo transportando la antorcha del Sport Aid 88 y conseguir que la gente se una a La Carrera Contra el Tiempo. Esto se conseguirá izando una bandera y encendiendo la llama en la antorcha de cada uno de los 6 continentes. \nEl juego tiene más de 100 escenarios, incluyendo lugares famosos, tales como las pirámides de Gizeh, el palacio de Buckingham, el monte Rushmore, el Kremlin y las cataratas del lago Victoria. \n¿Cuántos lugares podrás reconocer mientras juegas? \nComienzas el juego de madrugada en el campo de refugiados de El Mowheli, en Sudán, debiendo encontrar primero el aeropuerto. Utiliza el mapa del mundo para escoger tu destino y pulsa la tecla de Acción para ir hacia ese continente. Tu misión es izar la bandera y encender la llama con tu antorcha.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[1070,1073,10039,55752,1188,51485,26848,36608,74863,19174],"tags":[1,268435464,536872961,536875138,1073741828],"developers":[115],"publishers":[115],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[2049,4226],"themes":[1],"genres":[8],"first_release_date":599529600000,"platforms":[15,26,25],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":26,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1988","y":1988,"m":12}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uuvt8bwngj39hchyk0b8.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uuvt8bwngj39hchyk0b8","width":1000,"height":1265}},{"id":39133,"name":"Starstrike 2","slug":"starstrike-2","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/starstrike-2","created_at":1498120814372,"updated_at":1513004254264,"summary":"In Realtime's previous Starstrike game (not to be confused with Star Strike), the evil Outsiders attacked the Federation and had to be forced back. This time, the boot's on the other foot, as the Federation have sent their Starstrike II vehicles in to take them out. Armed with sophisticated computers, lasers and shields, all it needs is a good pilot, such as yourself. \n \nTwenty-two planets fall under Outsiders control, and each has grid-based defenses which must be taken out, complete with all their command computers and production droids. The planets are split into five groups, each of which can be chosen at the start of the game. \n \nThe combat is intense, and aims to create the likely feel of space combat, with lots of ducking and weaving to set up shots. The game features filled-in graphics, unlike the Elite-esque wireframes of the first game.","collection":5111,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"keywords":[534,3782],"themes":[34],"genres":[15],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/dgexmtalggjalz6umnhs.jpg","cloudinary_id":"dgexmtalggjalz6umnhs","width":150,"height":194}},{"id":39134,"name":"Super Robin Hood","slug":"super-robin-hood","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/super-robin-hood","created_at":1498120826916,"updated_at":1515580589585,"summary":"You will need skill and quick reflexes to survive in the dangerous \ncastle complex. Watch out for the guards who shoot bolts at you with their \ncrossbows, you can duck or jump to avoid them, or even run away. If you get \nhit you will lose vital HEALTH points. These start at 99 and if they fall \nbelow 00 you are a dead man! There are tablets lying around which will \nincrease your HEALTH points if you can get them. \n \nYou must collect all the hearts around the castle and then go to the \nEast Tower to save Maid Marian. However, to make progress through the castle \nyou have to get the keys needed to operate the mechanical mediaeval lifts \nwhich elevate you to different sections of the castle.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[37088,16468,26848,55752,10039,37094,26196,6985,26391,47823],"tags":[1,17,22,268435464,536871213,536872961,536873064,536875067,536875229,536875304,536875639,536879691,1073741828],"developers":[115],"publishers":[115],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[301,2049,2152,4155,4317,4392,4727,8779],"themes":[1,17,22],"genres":[8],"first_release_date":536371200000,"platforms":[15,26,25],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":26,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":567907200000,"region":1,"human":"1987","y":1987,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":536371200000,"region":1,"human":"1986","y":1986,"m":12}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/dwjdhmpcdi7jblbhwd47.jpg","cloudinary_id":"dwjdhmpcdi7jblbhwd47","width":1000,"height":1599}},{"id":39135,"name":"Super Pipeline II","slug":"super-pipeline-ii","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/super-pipeline-ii","created_at":1498120830540,"updated_at":1515671773947,"summary":"As Foreman Fred you must defend the pipework supply against the attacks from the manic power drills as they cause leaks and protect your workmen from gnawing caterpillars and ferocious hammers.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660