pocket\" game, in which you play by yourself or against a friend trying to pocket 6 balls. Players start with only 4 cues (scratching or failing to pocket a ball substracts from your total cues, reaching 0 means game over), and different ball effects are available by pressing the second button and selecting it with the joystick. \n \nEach of the 4 stages is hosted by a corresponding girl, who's only function (not that I'm complaining) is to strip when the level is cleared. Additional points and shots can be gained by pocketing balls in order, in computer-predetermined pockets, clearing special bonus tricks between stages, etc.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[11362,73075,9760,33603,36962,55888,65827,2015,32283,33383],"tags":[268435471],"category":0,"genres":[15],"first_release_date":633225600000,"platforms":[52],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":52,"date":633225600000,"region":8,"human":"1990-Jan-25","y":1990,"m":1}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/tn0fe6nox1ebnwqhmvgy.jpg","cloudinary_id":"tn0fe6nox1ebnwqhmvgy","width":800,"height":700},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rglpqsmw0cvwoodm9pwc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rglpqsmw0cvwoodm9pwc","width":800,"height":700}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gscakimjmky3ap6gdeeo.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gscakimjmky3ap6gdeeo","width":850,"height":1196}},{"id":39502,"name":"Tehkan World Cup","slug":"tehkan-world-cup","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/tehkan-world-cup","created_at":1498129458406,"updated_at":1500224640570,"summary":"Tehkan World Cup, aka. Tecmo Cup, is the first multi-player soccer game featuring a trackball controller. \nProgrammed by Michishito Ishizuka it was released to arcades in 1985 by Tehkan, Ltd., the former name of Tecmo, Inc. Its arrival coincided with the buildup to the 1986 FIFA World Cup. It featured the then colors of several of the world's top teams such as West Germany, Argentina and Brazil, although it did n