eat ships are arriving at major cities around the globe preparing to conquer and claim what is rightfully theirs... the human race. \n \nTo stop the invasion you must complete 4 separate missions by defeating the invading aliens that are abducting and mutating humans, snatching monuments and creating havoc in the world. The fate of the plant is in your hands!","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46892,41258,76246,19341,28029,32902,97018,96550,93794,88910],"tags":[268435461],"category":0,"genres":[5]},{"id":39625,"name":"Stakes Winner 2","slug":"stakes-winner-2","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/stakes-winner-2","created_at":1498133287011,"updated_at":1509955115195,"summary":"Like its predecessor, Stakes Winner 2 is a 2D horse racing game. Choosing from one of the game's selection of horses, players must compete in a series of races on different tracks to earn money and prestige. Each horse that players can select is rated according to speed, stamina, and burst. \n \nPlayers control their horses with the joystick and three buttons. Pressing the A button repeatedly keeps the horse accelerated with a slight drain of the stamina bar, while pressing the B button applies the rider crop to the horse. This results in a slight burst of speed at the cost of draining the horse's stamina bar faster.","popularity":1.666666666666667,"games":[46820,39665,101684,101567,101100,100907,100887,100879,100863,100832],"tags":[268435470],"category":0,"genres":[14],"first_release_date":821491200000,"platforms":[80,79],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":79,"date":822441600000,"region":2,"human":"1996-Jan-24","y":1996,"m":1},{"category":0,"platform":79,"date":822441600000,"region":5,"human":"1996-Jan-24","y":1996,"m":1},{"category":0,"platform":80,"date":821491200000,"region":5,"human":"1996-Jan-13","y":1996,"m":1}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/vzb105gqzckrefxd3jkg.jpg","cloudinary_id":"vzb105gqzckrefxd3jkg","width":850,"height":1183}},{"id":39626,"na