. You control a ship that can fire in multiple directions. Fly through the tunnels in either direction shooting all of the bad guys.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660,1070,23175,76438,16468],"tags":[1],"category":0,"themes":[1],"first_release_date":404956800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":404956800000,"region":8,"human":"1982-Nov-01","y":1982,"m":11}]},{"id":40627,"name":"Codebreaker","slug":"codebreaker","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/codebreaker","created_at":1498481969835,"updated_at":1503195182319,"summary":"This one's not for stupid people. The goal of codebreaker is to guess a 3 or 4 digit number in 12 tries. The computer lets you know when your on the right track with some vague clues. In the second game, NIM, you and your opponent strategically remove blocks in an attempt to be the one to remove the last block.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[19222,41348,10225,27266,14246,60044,236,27725,101980,101976],"tags":[268435465],"category":0,"genres":[9],"first_release_date":278726400000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":278726400000,"region":8,"human":"1978-Nov-01","y":1978,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jjgpbkddab7xuidnhoxj.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jjgpbkddab7xuidnhoxj","width":600,"height":830}},{"id":40628,"name":"Chase the Chuck Wagon","slug":"chase-the-chuck-wagon","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/chase-the-chuck-wagon","created_at":1498481971900,"updated_at":1515639708256,"summary":"In the 80's, the popular commercial for Purina dog food included a dog chasing a tiny chuckwagon across the kitchen floor. Inspired by this, Chase the Chuckwagon was produced by Spectravision and released as a promotional item from the Ralston Purina Company. Buy lots of dog food and you could own this. The simple rarity of this game combined with its historical coolness makes it one of the \"holy grail\" games. The object is to navigate the dog through a maze in an effort to reach the chuckwagon, while avoiding the dog catcher and other obstacles. If he makes it, an animation shows the dog chasing after the chuckwagon and stopping to eat the dog food that falls out of it.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[23175,59516,55289,25646,37022,25311,47823,37088,12579,25300],"tags":[1,268435487,536871599,536875727,536875939,536877803,536879868],"category":0,"keywords":[687,4815,5027,6891,8956],"themes":[1],"genres":[31],"first_release_date":436492800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":436492800000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Nov-01","y":1983,"m":11}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/mmjkuqxapvvil6kk4zdr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"mmjkuqxapvvil6kk4zdr","width":900,"height":636}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/viyzhnranipz6dcd9pjb.jpg","cloudinary_id":"viyzhnranipz6dcd9pjb","width":600,"height":810}},{"id":40629,"name":"Cathouse Blues","slug":"cathouse-blues","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cathouse-blues","created_at":1498481974881,"updated_at":1500244877300,"summary":"In Cathouse Blues, you are a horny guy who has to memorize which 7 houses the ladies of ill repute wander into. Grab some cash from the teller, and visit each woman. A visit will cost $20, at which time you'll find yourself in her bed. Score with her as many times as you can before you're forced to leave for the next. The cops are in pursuit as well as a mugger who wants your money. Visiting a wrong house will cause you to be temporarily immobilized (a sitting duck for the cops) as you figure out what to do next. The roles of the men and women are switched in Gigolo.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31],"first_release_date":404956800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":404956800000,"region":8,"human":"1982-Nov-01","y":1982,"m":11}]},{"id":40630,"name":"Bumper bash","slug":"bumper-bash","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/bumper-bash","created_at":1498481976679,"updated_at":1516170053483,"summary":"A pinball simulator, along the same lines as Atari's Midnight Magic. But this one differs in that it uses the buttons on two paddle controllers to work the flippers, giving it that real pinball feel.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[18467,36608,34919,50599,28530,24879,22149,19671,16468,23175],"tags":[1,268435486,536871846],"category":0,"keywords":[934],"themes":[1],"genres":[30],"first_release_date":436492800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":436492800000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Nov-01","y":1983,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/omoj0yuw5k87gnyrjd2p.jpg","cloudinary_id":"omoj0yuw5k87gnyrjd2p","width":200,"height":273}},{"id":40631,"name":"Boom Bang","slug":"boom-bang","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/boom-bang","created_at":1498481979090,"updated_at":1500244842850,"summary":"Bugs are crawling out of the sewers and are coming for you. Your defense: a bunch of potted plants hanging over your balcony. As the bugs climb the wall, push the pots over the edge and knock the bugs off. If six bugs get into your building through the window, they'll eat away at the foundation until the building drops a bit. Then the bugs will have a shorter wall to climb, and things get harder. This game is original, challenging, and pretty addictive. Get 75,000 points and earn the Crackpots patch.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46892,41258,76246,19341,28029,32902,97018,96550,93794,88910],"tags":[268435461],"category":0,"genres":[5],"first_release_date":404956800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":404956800000,"region":8,"human":"1982-Nov-01","y":1982,"m":11}]},{"id":40632,"name":"Bogey Blaster","slug":"bogey-blaster","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/bogey-blaster","created_at":1498481980769,"updated_at":1500244834343,"summary":"A simple flight simulator and dogfighting game. Shoot the planes, avoid the flak. You have a limited amount of ammuntion and fuel. Shoot down 10 planes and you can land to refuel, but you may lose ammo. You'll only be given as much ammunition as you successfully used to shoot down planes the last time up.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[46892,41258,76246,19341,28029,32902,97018,96550,93794,88910],"tags":[268435461],"category":0,"genres":[5],"first_release_date":404956800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":404956800000,"region":8,"human":"1982-Nov-01","y":1982,"m":11}]},{"id":40633,"name":"Big Bird's Egg Catch","slug":"big-birds-egg-catch","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/big-birds-egg-catch","created_at":1498481997404,"updated_at":1515587203029,"summary":"Two chickens are laying eggs. You'll know one's about to drop when a chicken stands up. As they drop down the chutes, Farmer Big Bird moves back and forth to catch them. Different chute patterns make the game more difficult. This kids game is based on the classic Sesame Street character. It is intended for use with the kids controller, which is an oversized keyboard controller into which you insert the included overlay for this game. If you don't have a kids controller, the keyboard controller works fine, but you'll have to figure out what the buttons do","collection":3194,"popularity":1.0,"games":[29173,23345,19376,55036,55590,18167,21063,19934,18918,19301],"tags":[34,268435465,268435471,536871446,536871570,536872140,536872475,536874694,536875088,536875209,536875291,536882367],"category":0,"keywords":[534,658,1228,1563,3782,4176,4297,4379,11455],"themes":[34],"genres":[9,15],"first_release_date":436492800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":436492800000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Nov-01","y":1983,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/xub7eyv7spqbjlsu70is.jpg","cloudinary_id":"xub7eyv7spqbjlsu70is","width":600,"height":817}},{"id":40634,"name":"Berenstain Bears","slug":"berenstain-bears","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/berenstain-bears","created_at":1498481999127,"updated_at":1515641748771,"summary":"Berenstain Bears comes with three different cassette tapes that are designed to be used with the Kid Vid Controller (originally packaged with Smurfs Save the Day - the only other Kid Vid game). The cartridge won't do much without the tapes. At the beginning of each game, Actual Factual Bear takes off while you control Brother Bear on his unicycle. Avoid the boulders and cross the bridge to reach one of the games, chosen by the particular tape you are listening to. The games are: \nBig Number Hunt: Catch the correct numbers as they fall from the tree \nGreat Letter Roundup: Catch the correct letters as they fall from the tree \nSpooky Spelling Bee: Spell a word by catching the letters falling from the tree","collection":4439,"popularity":1.0,"games":[27266,10730,78720,73664,73098,71964,71608,71546,70044,63812],"tags":[34,268435465,536871446,536872475,536875078],"category":0,"keywords":[534,1563,4166],"themes":[34],"genres":[9],"first_release_date":436492800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":436492800000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Nov-01","y":1983,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/tcivymgaf6qs5qewgphj.jpg","cloudinary_id":"tcivymgaf6qs5qewgphj","width":660,"height":871}},{"id":40635,"name":"Zoo Fun","slug":"zoo-fun","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/zoo-fun","created_at":1498482001371,"updated_at":1500244800344,"popularity":1.0,"games":[19222,11362,9760,33603,41348,36962,55888,73075,65827,10225],"tags":[268435465,268435471],"category":0,"genres":[9,15]},{"id":40636,"name":"Star Wars: Ewok Adventure","slug":"star-wars-ewok-adventure","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/star-wars-ewok-adventure","created_at":1498482003733,"updated_at":1500244774912,"summary":"You take the role of an EWOK in this thrilling game based on scenes from RETURN OF THE JEDI. Now a member of the Rebel cause, you must hang glide over dangerous territory in order to reach the Imperial shield generator. Your mission: to blow it \napart! But as you swoop through the forest, IMPERIAL STORMTROOPERS, AT-ST's and BIKER SCOUTS will try to shoot you down. Hurl rocks at the enemy as you avoid their fire and close in on the shield generator.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660,1070,23175,76438,16468],"tags":[1],"category":0,"themes":[1],"first_release_date":854755200000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":854755200000,"region":8,"human":"1997-Feb-01","y":1997,"m":2}]},{"id":40637,"name":"Obelix","slug":"obelix","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/obelix","created_at":1498482005216,"updated_at":1519410190316,"summary":"CAESAR'S GALLING DEFEAT \n \nThe year: 50 B.C. The place: a Gaulish village near the Roman outposts of Totorum, Aquarium, Laudanum, and Compendium. Here we find the last outpost of resistance against the legions of Julius Caesar. And who are the leaders of these indomitable fighters against the mighty Roman empire? Who has the gall to oppose Caesar's will? Why, none other than a humble menhir deliveryman named Obelix, and his small but shrewd friend, Asterix.","popularity":1.0,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660,1070,23175,76438,16468],"tags":[1],"category":0,"themes":[1],"first_release_date":412905600000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":412905600000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Feb-01","y":1983,"m":2}]},{"id":40638,"name":"Donald Duck's Speedboat","slug":"donald-ducks-speedboat","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/donald-ducks-speedboat","created_at":1498482007357,"updated_at":1516585789174,"summary":"Donald has entered the Duckburg boat race and has taken to the sea with his speedboat. The objective is to steer the boat away from the obstacles along the way to the finish line and do so as fast as possible without losing pressure on the throttle. The game takes place across multiple screens which each presents its own obstacle patterns and challenges.","collection":2986,"popularity":1.0,"games":[40470,28856,54789,55192,36662,78017,80095,65413,45069,19419],"tags":[268435466,536875054,536875069,536875074,536875079,536875292,536875417],"category":0,"keywords":[4142,4157,4162,4167,4380,4505],"genres":[10],"first_release_date":412905600000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":412905600000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Feb-01","y":1983,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rxuaclf5shgnh8ukkizp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rxuaclf5shgnh8ukkizp","width":166,"height":200}},{"id":40639,"name":"Dumbo's Flying Circus","slug":"dumbos-flying-circus","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dumbos-flying-circus","created_at":1498482009661,"updated_at":1500244723745,"summary":"Dumbo's Flying Circus was scheduled to be part of Atari's children's series (which included characters from Peanuts, Sesame Street, Disney, Muppets, and Garfield), but for one reason or another it never saw the light of day. Atari advertised Dumbo in European Atari catalogs and even had a prototype box made, so the decision to shelve it must have been made quite late. Even though Dumbo was developed as a children's game, the gameplay is quite difficult which may be the reason why it was never released.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[14605,17469,75586,25130,43130,23175,28277,63734,29646,27266],"tags":[268435487],"category":0,"genres":[31]},{"id":40640,"name":"Bachelorette Party","slug":"bachelorette-party","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/bachelorette-party","created_at":1498482011032,"updated_at":1513003830444,"summary":"Rescue a damsel in distress from being burned alive by moving around in your helicopter and putting out the flame with your fire hose. Meanwhile, avoid the rocks being thrown at you by the bad dudes. When you've nearly extinguished the flames, the woman will begin jumping up and down. If you swoop down, she'll latch on to your \"joystick\" with her mouth, and you can fly her off to safety before the flames move in on her. If you save her, you will be rewarded with a dirty little animation. The male and female roles of this game are switched in Jungle Fever. \n \nBachelorette Party is an \"x-rated\" version of Breakout. Move the Spanish fly so that the woman comes in contact with it. She will then ricochet toward the men and \"score\" with each one she touches. She will then bounce back toward the fly. If you miss her, you lose a turn. The fun part is watching the men's willies go up and down as she flies toward them. The roles of the men and women are switched in Bachelor Party.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[44242,24491,28465,75579,75275,34919,75102,33603,36962,55888],"tags":[268435469],"category":0,"keywords":[343,960,1961,4159],"themes":[1,42],"genres":[13],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gc2qsdosdknocbhm9zgd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gc2qsdosdknocbhm9zgd","width":600,"height":747}},{"id":40641,"name":"Exocet","slug":"exocet","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/exocet","created_at":1498482156424,"updated_at":1515654239115,"summary":"In Exocet, you first pilot a spacecraft over the surface, shooting the defense towers in your path. The larger towers are too large to fly around, and they must be hit at the point where they fire. When you have traveled a particular distance, you will find an opening to the underground passage. There you continue to destroy the various things flying around.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[68287,28029,36950,64204,142,27314,71455,25300,27523,11253],"tags":[1,18,268435461,536871644,536871882,536871937,536871971],"category":0,"keywords":[732,970,1025,1059],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[5],"first_release_date":412905600000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":412905600000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Feb-01","y":1983,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hd615vl8hwgvmnhqzmyn.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hd615vl8hwgvmnhqzmyn","width":600,"height":830}},{"id":40642,"name":"Eli's Ladder","slug":"elis-ladder","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/elis-ladder","created_at":1498482158245,"updated_at":1500244987403,"summary":"Eli's Ladder is an educational game aimed at children, where math problems need to be solved to help Eli and his crew climb a ladder to his space ship so they can then journey to the Moon. The game included a wall chart and stickers designed to help motivate children progress through the problems. This is one of the rarest Atari 2600 games and apparently saw fairly limited distribution.","popularity":1.0,"games":[19222,41348,10225,27266,14246,60044,236,27725,101980,101976],"tags":[268435465],"category":0,"genres":[9]},{"id":40643,"name":"Dragon Treasure","slug":"dragon-treasure","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dragon-treasure","created_at":1498482160306,"updated_at":1500244978792,"summary":"Dragon Treasure is a Canadian-released copy of Imagic's Dragonfire. \n \nThe goal of Dragonfire is to avoid the dragon's fireballs and capture the king's treasure. In the first screen, you run across a bridge, ducking and jumping over fireballs. Then, in the treasure room, you pick up the various treasures, avoiding the dragon's fireballs, and leave through the door you came in. Then you start again. Although Dragonfire is a novel game, it gets boring pretty quickly.","popularity":1.0,"category":0},{"id":40644,"name":"Dragon Defender","slug":"dragon-defender","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dragon-defender","created_at":1498482162850,"updated_at":1500244970299,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0},{"id":40645,"name":"Dice Puzzle","slug":"dice-puzzle","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dice-puzzle","created_at":1498482164802,"updated_at":1516743369058,"summary":"If you enjoy games like Rubik's Cube, then you'll like this one. The object of Dice Puzzle is to get all 16 dice to show the same number. You accomplish this by clicking on a column or row, which advances all of the numbers in that column or row by one (of course six advances to one). See how quickly (or in how many moves) you can do it.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[25222,60044,14047,74753,74727,71260,71254,70899,66270,63839],"tags":[34,268435465,536871446,536873787],"category":0,"keywords":[534,2875],"themes":[34],"genres":[9],"first_release_date":436492800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":436492800000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Nov-01","y":1983,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/vbq8akevzdlcycdmiwae.jpg","cloudinary_id":"vbq8akevzdlcycdmiwae","width":600,"height":808}},{"id":40646,"name":"Demolition Herby","slug":"demolition-herby","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/demolition-herby","created_at":1498482166206,"updated_at":1500244953312,"summary":"Demolition Herby is basically the same as Amidar by Parker Brothers', though in this case, you control a car that's being chased by other cars. When you drive around a box, it fills in. Fill in all of the boxes before you run out of gas or crash into another car. The other cars can also erase the work you've done. If you're in a tight spot, hit the button to shift into gas-guzzlin' overdrive. As the game progresses, the speed and intelligence of the other drivers increase.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"category":0,"first_release_date":404956800000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":404956800000,"region":8,"human":"1982-Nov-01","y":1982,"m":11}]},{"id":40647,"name":"Video Life","slug":"video-life","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/video-life","created_at":1498482169813,"updated_at":1515669648883,"summary":"Video Life is a rare video game for the Atari 2600. It is a version of the zero-player cellular automaton known as Conway's Game of Life. Video Life was only available through a special mail order offer to owners of CommaVid's Magicard, which itself is considered to be one of the rarest Atari 2600 cartridges ever released. According to original CommaVid co-owner Irwin Gaines, only 20 cartridges or less of Video Life were ever made. Editors of AtariAge estimate approximately 500 cartridges were produced. A report in the Chicago Reader by Jeffrey Felshman estimates that cartridges would sell for as much $3000 at the time.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[48799,46937,40905,40903,40897,40887,19222,27266,41348,73189],"tags":[34,268435465,536871446],"category":0,"keywords":[534],"themes":[34],"genres":[9],"first_release_date":360201600000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":360201600000,"region":8,"human":"1981-Jun-01","y":1981,"m":6}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/m9qplkwew2ickyh1vwe2.jpg","cloudinary_id":"m9qplkwew2ickyh1vwe2","width":600,"height":817}},{"id":40648,"name":"Video Reflex","slug":"video-reflex","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/video-reflex","created_at":1498482171437,"updated_at":1515576695206,"summary":"This game was originally packaged with Video Jogger and the Foot Craz Activity Pad. When a bug appears in one of the boxes, step on it quickly or lose a life. But if a butterfly appears, DON'T step on it or lose a life. You can end up jumping around pretty fast. You can also play this game with a joystick, but it's not as fun.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[36608,34919,55715,22690,14713,16468,23175,40524,59516,28029],"tags":[1,268435470,536872407,536875258,536876120],"category":0,"keywords":[1495,4346,5208],"themes":[1],"genres":[14],"first_release_date":412905600000,"platforms":[59],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":59,"date":412905600000,"region":8,"human":"1983-Feb-01","y":1983,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload