over tools, the wheel, weapons, or even fire. Each level in the game will have a given task to help in this, and you are allotted a number of characters who must accomplish the task. The player can switch from person to person while moving the characters around each scrolling puzzle, and teamwork is essential to success.","popularity":1.0,"category":0,"first_release_date":760060800000,"platforms":[62],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":62,"date":760060800000,"region":8,"human":"1994-Feb-01","y":1994,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lfnzvdmw94acb4yuxej1.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lfnzvdmw94acb4yuxej1","width":1521,"height":2100}},{"id":40802,"name":"Atari Karts","slug":"atari-karts","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/atari-karts","created_at":1498488650566,"updated_at":1515663124679,"summary":"A go-cart free for all! In Atari Karts you'll race around the track with some of the craziest creatures around. Watch out for the objects lying on the road. Some are bonuses that will help you get ahead, but those hazards can be nasty. They'll cause you to slow down or mess with your driving controls. Try to outdistance your competition and finish fourth or better to move on to the next course. Kids of all ages will love this game!","popularity":1.0,"games":[58785,40470,28856,26709,67625,42277,50695,54789,69725,49004],"tags":[268435466,536871192,536874337,536875069,536875093,536875117,536875128,536875955,536876788,536876927,536877097,536877930],"category":0,"keywords":[280,3425,4157,4181,4205,4216,5043,5876,6015,6185,7018],"genres":[10],"first_release_date":822096000000,"platforms":[62],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":62,"date":822096000000,"region":8,"human":"1996-Jan-20","y":1996,"m":1}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/k0vsfqah1siathnzzn6n.jpg","cloudinary_id":"k0vsfqah1siathnzzn6n","width":1521,"height":2100}},{"id":40803,"name":"Cybermorph","slug":"cybermorph","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cybermorph","created_at":1498488655126,"updated_at":1521890659981,"summary":"Cybermorph was the first game released for Atari's Jaguar console. It's a 3D sci-fi shoot-'em-up. The story goes like this: The evil Pernitia Empire is swallowing up the galaxy's planets left and right. What's worse, the resistance forces have had their secret weapons stolen from them and put into pods spread out on many different planets. You must pilot the T-Griffon morphing attack craft to each planet and recover the pods to stop the Pernitians. \n \nSo, in each planet, or level, you must collect a certain number of pods and make it to the exit before the enemies shoot you down. Fortunately, there are power-ups that can strategically enhance the T-Griffon's offensive capabilities. After clearing 8 planets, you take on a boss creature/ship before moving on to the next sector. There are 4 levels like this to clear, each with progressively increasing difficulty.","popularity":1.0,"games":[46892,41258,76246,19341,28029,32902,97018,96550,93794,88910],"tags":[268435461],"category":0,"genres":[5],"first_release_date":728524800000,"platforms":[62],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":62,"date":728524800000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Feb-01","y":1993,"m":2}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/kaxi6xhqnltpupntw3pp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"kaxi6xhqnltpupntw3pp","width":1533,"height":2095}},{"id":40804,"name":"Club Drive","slug":"club-drive","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/club-drive","created_at":1498488671099,"updated_at":1523763079998,"summary":"Sure, you've always wanted to blaze down the streets of San Francisco in a souped-up hot rod, just like in those action movies. But have you ever wanted to scramble across the living room floor playing tag in a minature racing car with a buddy? Or plow through an Old West town in a futuristic speed machine picking up randomly placed energy Powerballs? Strap in and join the 64-bit club!","popularity":1.0,"games":[58785,40470,80441,73154