nd its the players job to see that this incursion is stopped. \n \nThe game features flying saucers that drop bombs, craters that must be jumped, boulders that must be blasted, incoming missiles, tanks and land mines. The buggy tracks left to right across the screen, it can accelerate, decelerate, fire missiles and jump but it cannot go backwards. Points are scored for enemies destroyed and distance travelled. The game records the top five scores for the gaming session.","popularity":1.0,"games":[36608,2940,40524,34919,71581,29660,1070,23175,76438,16468],"tags":[1],"category":0,"themes":[1]},{"id":40931,"name":"Spy vs. Spy: The Island Caper","slug":"spy-vs-spy-the-island-caper","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/spy-vs-spy-the-island-caper","created_at":1498490439653,"updated_at":1515649372470,"summary":"A follow-up to the first Spy vs Spy game now sees the spies stranded on a desert island. This time, instead of the four items which allow you to leave for the airport, the spies must try to collect 3 pieces of a missile. \n \nThere are new traps and a single gun to take part in combat, rather than the big sticks of the previous game.","collection":4412,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[65832,19083,19934,11588,29173,12773,76731,25311,36868,76098],"tags":[1,27,268435471,536871262,536872098,536872131,536873771,536874694,536875074,536875222,536875717,536875942,536876381],"category":0,"keywords":[350,1186,1219,2859,3782,4162,4310,4805,5030,5469],"themes":[1,27],"genres":[15],"first_release_date":491702400000,"platforms":[15],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":15,"date":491702400000,"region":8,"human":"1985-Aug-01","y":1985,"m":8}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Nangoku Shirei!! Spy vs Spy","comment":"Other"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/szdqqcytlvgioy7lw0du.jpg","cloudinary_id":"szdqqcytlvgioy7lw0du","width":1744,"height":2460}},{"id":40932,"name":"Retrograde","slug":"retrograde","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/retrograde","cr