rading cards involved characters and enemies from Metal Gear, Metal Gear 2: Solid Snake. Metal Gear Solid, Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty, Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater, Metal Gear Solid 4: Guns of the Patriots, Metal Gear Solid: Peace Walker, Metal Gear Rising: Revengeance and Metal Gear Solid V: Ground Zeroes. Besides cards relating to the Metal Gear series, there were also cards related to Zone of the Enders, another series of games by Kojima Productions and collaboration cards with other GREE game series such as Cerberus Jihad and Dragon Collection.  \n  \nThe game's official website was launched on August 30, 2012.  \n  \nOn October 2013, Konami announced via the Social Ops website that the servers of the game would come to an end. The final mission was downloadable on October 31, 2013 til November 13, 2013. The game was then removed from being downloaded on December 13, 2013 and the service ended for good on January 31, 2014. All players unused credits from the \"Metal Gear Solid Coin\" bank was refunded.","collection":2128,"franchise":463,"franchises":[463],"popularity":2.333333333333333,"games":[36608,34919,9760,40524,23175,20041,16468,1070,2940,68324],"tags":[1,23,1073741826],"developers":[2670,170],"publishers":[129],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[2],"game_modes":[2],"themes":[1,23],"first_release_date":1354752000000,"status":5,"platforms":[34,39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1354752000000,"region":5,"human":"2012-Dec-06","y":2012,"m":12},{"category":0,"platform":34,"date":1354752000000,"region":5,"human":"2012-Dec-06","y":2012,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"MGS SOP"}],"videos":[{"name":"Gameplay video","video_id":"YqR-cg0eGtg"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/olpleezf8zr1dcr8zxnp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"olpleezf8zr1dcr8zxnp","width":350,"height":487},"websites":[{"category":3,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metal_Gear_Solid:_Social_Ops"},{"category":2,"url":"http://metalgear.wikia.