nsists of three energy points, but in the course of the game the energy supply can be raised. If the knight passes a rune stone, there is an important hint to be read. \n \nFurthermore there is a map of the castle's labyrinth, which shows an overview of the rooms that you have already visited. In the lower right of the screen the name of the currently entered room or area is displayed. The energy and coin display is at the lower left of the screen","popularity":3.0,"games":[1070,38305,1073,1188,89495,51942,51247,51203,50992,50924],"tags":[268435464],"developers":[14028],"category":0,"genres":[8],"first_release_date":1249084800000,"platforms":[15],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":15,"date":1249084800000,"region":8,"human":"2009-Aug-01","y":2009,"m":8}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hxpju9k6dueqpknyar2k.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hxpju9k6dueqpknyar2k","width":774,"height":540},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/j5r4giywysu2ceeslzed.jpg","cloudinary_id":"j5r4giywysu2ceeslzed","width":777,"height":503},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/pfre4xizorvmmaiugwz8.jpg","cloudinary_id":"pfre4xizorvmmaiugwz8","width":778,"height":539},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rm5lvbo2irbe9yx46sj3.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rm5lvbo2irbe9yx46sj3","width":814,"height":565},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yllw1un2p5aiigrxjdcu.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yllw1un2p5aiigrxjdcu","width":814,"height":565}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/mgw1uu3yfystirbkelgs.jpg","cloudinary_id":"mgw1uu3yfystirbkelgs","width":400,"height":304}},{"id":41119,"name":"Knight Games 2: Space Trilogy","slug":"knight-games-2-space-trilogy","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/knight-games-2-space-trilogy","created_at":1498812570764,"updated_at":1501820614548,"summary":"Knight Games 2: Space Trilogy is the sequel to Knight Games. Set in the year 3002, it consists of three different futuristic gam